{
  "texts": [
    "Hence, we only used the information available to the participants in the source study to generate justification texts.",
    "Moreover, we provided ChatGPT with exactly the same context in which each of the ten selected human stimuli was collected.",
    "The human and AI stimuli can therefore be related to each other.",
    "We developed a strict protocol for generating text using AI tools.",
    "The full protocol is available in Supplementary Appendix SA."
  ]
}